<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
    <head>
        <meta charset="UTF-8"/>
        <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
        <title>EMA623_06_SU_0004_s</title>

        <!-- 공통 js-->
        <script src="../../common_contents/common/js/app.js"></script>

        <!-- 공통 css-->
        <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_contents/common/css/app.css"/>

        <!-- 개별 -->
        <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_contents/css/ema623_common.css"/>
        <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_contents/css/ema623_06.css"/>
    </head>
    <body>
        <div id="app_wrap" class="ema623_06_SU_0004">
            <section class="title type2">
                <h2 data-head="2_pink" lang="y">쌓기나무로 만든 모양을 층별로 나타낸 모양입니다. 쌓기나무의 개수와 위, 앞, 옆에서 본 모양을 알아봅시다.</h2>
            </section>

            <section class="contents paging_layout">
                <article class="page page_1">
                    <div class="img_row">
                        <div class="img_wrap"><img src="../../common_contents/img/EMA623_06_SU/0004_contents.png" alt=""/></div>

                        <div class="input_area">
                            <div>
                                <h3 lang="y">똑같은 모양으로 만드는 데 필요한 쌓기나무는 몇 개인가요?</h3>
                                <!-- 단답형 -->
                                <div class="question_box gap_8 justify_center">
                                    <div class="input_wrap short_width">
                                        <math-field
                                            data-answer-single="10"
                                            placeholder="​"
                                            contenteditable="true"
                                            tabindex="0"
                                            id="page_4-math-field-3"
                                            sound="false"
                                            math-mode-space="\:"
                                            smart-fence="off"
                                            smart-superscript="off"></math-field>
                                        <div class="text_hint">10
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                    <span lang="y">개</span>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </article>
                <article class="page page_2">
                    <div class="img_row building_blocks">
                        <div class="img_wrap"><img src="../../common_contents/img/EMA623_06_SU/0004_contents.png" alt=""/></div>

                        <div class="input_area">
                            <div>
                                <h3 lang="y">쌓기나무로 만들면 어떤 모양이 될지 예상해 보고, 만들어 보세요</h3>
                                <div class="gray_box">
                                    <div class="box_title">
                                        <button class="minus"></button>쌓기나무 개수<button class="plus"></button>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="wood_box_area">
                                        <button class="wood_box"></button>
                                    </div>

                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </article>
                <article class="page page_3">
                    <div class="img_row building_blocks">
                        <div class="img_wrap">
                          <img src="../../common_contents/img/EMA623_06_SU/0004_contents.png" alt=""/>
                        </div>
                        
                        <div class="input_area">
                          <div>
                            <h3 lang="y">위, 앞, 옆에서 본 모양을 각각 그려 보세요</h3>
                            <img src="../../common_contents/img/EMA623_06_SU/0004_img04_contents.png" alt=""/>
                                
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </article>

                <div class="btn_area">
                    <button class="btnType key">입력타입토글</button>
                    <button class="btnReset">리셋</button>
                    <button class="btnCheck">확인</button>
                    <button class="btnSubmit">제출</button>
                </div>
            </section>
        </div>
    </body>
</html>